name: Veiny Breast [BETA]
description:
Tag - Veiny_Breast

I'm making a Discord Server. Join if you want - https://discord.gg/3mGXrS87cE
Also, I need helpers to make Free Requested Loras / My Idea's Loras. Join Discord if you wanna help. this will be not paid as I don't earn anything from it or from anywhere.

Important -

  • This is the BETA Model. It can produce good results but here are the settings to get those. I'll appreciate your Reviews and Likes, but please don't downrate it too much its beta.

  • I couldn't find Datasets to train on so I had to draw them manually. I generated tons of Boobs images and then manually drew veins on them.

  • The Veins converge to become Sweat Drops when completed. So you have to put sweat, sweat_drops, water_drops, water, sweat on breast in negative prompts.

  • If you use tons of Negative Embedding it will always result in sweats. So don't use a lot of Negative Textual Inversion Embeddings.

Please Review and Like this Model if you appreciate it. The least you can do to keep me motivated.

Also, I'll appreciate your support on my Patreon and ko-fi.

Here is a Form you can request me Lora there (for Free too)

https://forms.gle/h9iuLCCnaEs6W9ZB8
